about.summary: Programmatic interface to the Web Service methods provided by the National 'Phenology' Network (<https://usanpn.org/>), which includes data on various life history events that occur at specific times.

Programmatic interface to the Web Service methods provided by the National 'Phenology' Network (<https://usanpn.org/>), which includes data on various life history events that occur at specific times.

name: r-rnpn
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.2.8.0" %}

{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-rnpn
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/rnpn_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/rnpn/rnpn_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 5c8882542cd18efbb13db8318b8534e1986c0964f9051a5928c51cedaead6aeb

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 0
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-xml
    - r-curl
    - r-data.table >=1.9.6
    - r-httr >=1.1.0
    - r-jsonlite >=0.9.19
    - r-magrittr
    - r-plyr
    - r-raster
    - r-rgdal
    - r-sp >=1.1_0
    - r-tibble

  run:
    - r-base
    - r-xml
    - r-curl
    - r-data.table >=1.9.6
    - r-httr >=1.1.0
    - r-jsonlite >=0.9.19
    - r-magrittr
    - r-plyr
    - r-raster
    - r-rgdal
    - r-sp >=1.1_0
    - r-tibble

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('rnpn')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('rnpn')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/usa-npn/rnpn/ (devel)
  license: MIT
  summary: Programmatic interface to the Web Service methods provided by the National 'Phenology' Network (<https://usanpn.org/>), which includes data on various life history events that occur at specific times.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT'
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - thewchan
